OL,6,FA 74-year-old man from Northop has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed after using controlling
OL,8,Fand coercive behaviour against his
OL,9,Fdisabled wife.
OL,11,FGeoffrey Pennington is said to have
OL,12,F"tormented", Amanda Jane Lloyd, 65,
OL,13,Fover a three year period, even
OL,14,Fthreatening to 'take her teeth out and
OL,15,Fbite off one of her ears.'
OL,17,Fheard that Pennington's crimes were
OL,18,Feventually uncovered after Ms Lloyd
OL,19,Fmade secret recordings of him
OL,20,Fattacking her, which she took to the
OL,21,Fpolice.
