OL,4,C'wife's teeth and bite off ear' jailed
OL,6,FProsecutor David Mainstone said that
OL,7,Fthe behaviour towards Ms Lloyd, who
OL,8,Fhas a range of health issues including
OL,9,Fosteoporosis, amounted to a
OL,10,F"disability hate crime."
OL,12,FIn court he detailed Ms Lloyd's ordeal
OL,13,Fsaying that on 16 August last year,
OL,14,FPennington of Glan yr Eglwys, was
OL,15,Foutside their home talking to a
OL,16,Fneighbour. Ms Lloyd informed him his
OL,17,Fdinner was ready but he told her:
OL,18,F"Don't you f***** tell me when to come
OL,19,Fin."
