OL,6,FHe is also said to have 'showered her
OL,7,Fwith spittle until her face was
OL,8,Fsoaking, tried to remove her teeth and
OL,9,Ftold her he'd bite off her left ear'
OL,11,FMs Lloyd was said to have been left
OL,12,Ffeeling "utterly worthless" but
OL,13,Fmanaged to ring 999.
OL,15,FMr Mainstone said Pennington then held
OL,16,Fa serrated knife to Ms Lloyd's throat,
OL,17,Ftelling her: "Right b****, I'm going
OL,18,Fto kill you and then myself." However
OL,19,Fthe police arrived in time to arrest
OL,20,Fhim.
