OL,6,FIn an interview the defendant said his
OL,7,Fwife was an alcoholic and regularly
OL,8,Ffalls over and gets injured. In a
OL,9,Fvictim statement Ms Lloyd said she is
OL,10,Fafraid of him.
OL,12,FShe said he has "completely destroyed
OL,13,Fher" and her quality of life is "non-
OL,14,Fexistent". She said she had been
OL,15,Fkicked so hard by her husband in the
OL,16,Fpast that she developed cellulitis.
