OL,6,FBut he said his client had been a
OL,7,Fcarer for his wife and the behaviour
OL,8,Fwas not motivated by hate. He added
OL,9,Fthat they had both become depressed
OL,10,Fduring the lockdown period as
OL,11,Frestrictions impacted their routines,
OL,12,Fgoing out and on holidays.
OL,14,FThe judge His Honour Niclas Parry told
OL,15,Fhim: "Over three years you tormented
OL,16,Fyour victim mentally and physically, a
OL,17,Fvictim who is vulnerable owing to
OL,18,Fserious health problems.
OL,20,F"She has been subjected to disgusting
OL,21,Fverbal abuse."
