OL,6,FThe judge added that the recordings
OL,7,Fwere a testament to her torment but
OL,8,Fsaid it was not a disability hate
OL,9,Fcrime.
OL,11,FJailing Pennington for 28 months, the
OL,12,Fjudge also imposed an indefinite
OL,13,Frestraining order prohibiting him from
OL,14,Fcontacting Ms Lloyd directly or
OL,15,Findirectly, going to her street or
OL,16,Freferring to her on social media.
